{"title":"背诵课文","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":7,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-3518","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>这道题是《C神背单词》的强化版。<br>一天，Bob去背积累了一个学期的课文（就是一篇好几页的那种），Bob整天想着打LOL，哪有心思去背课文呢~</p><p><br></p><p>“是时候用一下我的必杀技了！”他说道。</p><p>Bob可以用一种方法背课文。每篇课文有a[i]个字，他每个字需要背k秒。不过，他每背完一篇课文，速度k就会加快一秒（就是k-1）。不过他不是神，每个字至少要背1秒。</p><p><br></p><p>现在他有n篇课文要背，每篇课文有a[i]个字。请你求出他最快背完所有课文的时间。</p><p>P.s. 本题输入量较大，请使用正确的输入语句读入数据。<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行两个整数n和k，两个整数间用一个空格隔开。</p><p>接下来一行，有n个整数，之间用一个字符隔开，表示每篇课文的长度。<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一个整数，表示Bobby的最优方案。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span style=\"\">2 3</span></p><p><span style=\"\">4 1</span><span style=\"\"></span><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span style=\"\"> 11</span><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1 &lt;= n,k &lt;= 500000<br>1 &lt;= a[i] &lt;= n</p><p>你敢挑战一次过吗？</p><p>注意：请按正确格式输出。<br>\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}